Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎(かいざき)）うっ… ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（すみれ）ん… 気がついた？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.09,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.51,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,This is the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:01.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,保健室よ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.26,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,You two were found\Ncollapsed by the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:03.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたたち 階段で倒れてたの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:05.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）うっ…\N（すみれ）何があったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:05.72,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:07.73,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,Did you miss your step?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:08.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,階段 踏み外した？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:09.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:11.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）\Nはい ちょっと 滑ったみたいで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:11.94,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I guess I sorta slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:15.78,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,Kaizaki-kun, you shielded \NKariu-san from the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:15.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（すみれ）海崎君\N狩生(かりう)さんをかばう形になってたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:18.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やるじゃない\Nさすが 男の子！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:16.69,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,Nicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:18.61,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:21.70,Blue Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7}* Actually 27
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:21.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）ドスッ！\N男の… 子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.16,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:26.04,Italics Dialogue,Teacher,0,0,0,,Inukai-sensei, Inukai-sensei, \Nplease come to the staff room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:24.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（教師）\Nえー… 犬飼(いぬかい)先生 犬飼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:25.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,職員室までお願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:27.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（すみれ）\Nん… ああ ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.12,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:32.33,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll be back in a minute. \NCan you stay with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:29.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生 ちょっと行ってくるから—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:32.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生さんのそばに\Nいてあげてくれる？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.75,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:34.84,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:38.42,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,Your classmate, Hishiro-san, let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:38.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じクラスの日代さんが\N知らせてくれたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.51,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,She carried your stuff here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと あなたたちの荷物も\N運んでくれたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.89,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank her later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:44.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度 お礼を言っておきなさいね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.56,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Hishiro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）日代さんが…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.27,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I knew it... that was Hishiro-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:54.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）\Nやっぱり あれは 日代さんの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で 狩生が持ってたんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:57.19,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Why did Kariu have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.70,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,What was she trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする気だったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:04.53,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0,0,0,,She's got top sales again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男性社員）また あいつが\N営業トップだとさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:08.16,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0,0,0,,We'll lose face if we let\Na woman trounce us like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:08.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男性社員）女に ここまで\Nやられちゃ 俺らの顔が立たねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:11.17,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0,0,0,,Why won't she just quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:11.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男性社員）つか なかなか\N辞めねえな あいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:13.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺らのこと 気づいてないんかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.17,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0,0,0,,Hasn't she worked it out yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.96,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0,0,0,,With all we've done? She knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男性社員）\Nいや あんだけやったら—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:15.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがに気づいてんじゃね？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男性社員）おい お前ら\N新人の前でやめろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.80,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0,0,0,,Knock it off. The new guy's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:19.88,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:22.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男性社員）ああ 海崎の教育係\Nあいつだったっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.47,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0,0,0,,She's in charge of his training, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.35,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0,0,0,,Don't rat us out, Kaizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:25.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男性社員）\N変な告げ口はすんなよ 海崎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.60,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（佐伯(さいき)）申し訳ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.81,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0,0,0,,We'll make absolutely sure \Nnothing like this happens again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:32.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今後 このようなミスはないように\N気をつけますので—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:35.02,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0,0,0,,Please, let us make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:35.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なにとぞ\Nよろしくお願いいたします
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:40.36,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You know this mess wasn't your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:40.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）今回のミス\N先輩のせいじゃないですよ 絶対！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:43.07,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,We went over the order several times
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この前 俺に やり方\N教えてくれるために—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:46.16,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,while you were showing me the ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:46.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何度も 一緒に確認した\N発注書じゃないですか！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.03,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Someone must've...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）きっと誰かが…\N（佐伯）知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:47.79,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:53.25,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Doesn't it make you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:53.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怒ったりとか… しないんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:57.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（佐伯）人を落とすことで 自分が\N上がろうだなんて むなしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:57.50,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0,0,0,,Knocking others down to gain an advantage\Nis a fruitless endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:03:59.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうすることでしか\N勝ち目がないって—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:02.42,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0,0,0,,It means they've given up \Non winning any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分であきらめちゃってる\Nってことだもん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.26,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0,0,0,,At first,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなね…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.60,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0,0,0,,we all competed fair and square. \NIt was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（佐伯）最初は 正々堂々\N競い合って すごく楽しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.10,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0,0,0,,But then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに いつの間にか—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:15.98,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0,0,0,,somehow we went from rivals to enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:16.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライバルじゃなくて\N敵になっちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:23.45,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0,0,0,,Seeing hard workers turn out \Nlike that doesn't make me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:19.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（佐伯）怒るより何より—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:23.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張ってた人が そういうふうに\N変わってしまうのを見るのは—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.78,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すごく 悲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.24,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0,0,0,,...very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.12,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Were you trying to bully her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）嫌がらせしようとしたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.62,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,A hard worker like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張り屋のお前が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.25,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Oh. Are you awake, Kariu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）おっ 気がついたか 狩生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:43.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）おっ おい\Nあんま 急に動くな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.17,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Hey, no sudden movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:48.72,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Apparently, Hishiro-san found us\Nand let the teachers know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:48.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代さんが\N先生に知らせてくれたらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:52.93,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure she took that \Ngreen bag home with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:52.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,緑のかばんは 多分\N日代さんが持って帰ったんだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.44,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,That bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:01.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのかばん やっぱり\N日代さんのだったんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:01.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,It was Hishiro-san's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.36,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Why did you have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:03.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で 狩生が持ってた？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.24,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Don't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げるな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,答えろ 狩生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.20,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Answer me, Kariu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.04,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You steal anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）何か取ったのか？\N（狩生）違う！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.04,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.17,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:24.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少し… 困らせてやろうって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:24.26,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I just wanted to trouble her a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:28.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこかに 隠してやろうって\N思っただけで…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.22,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I was gonna hide it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:29.64,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）何で？\N（狩生）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:32.89,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:32.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）何でだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:36.73,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Have you given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:36.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな嫌がらせを\Nすることでしか もう—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:39.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代さんには勝ち目がないって\Nあきらめたからか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.90,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Do you think harassing her is\Nthe only way you'll beat her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.19,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）言うの？\N（海崎）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:48.78,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Are you gonna tell her I tried to\Nharass her because I was jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）あたしが\Nくだらない しっと心で—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:47.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌がらせをしようとしたって—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:48.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.74,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You're close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海崎 仲いいもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,That's why you knew it was her bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:53.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから あのかばんが\N日代のだって気づいたし—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怒ってるんでしょ あたしのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.87,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,and that's why you're mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:06:01.42,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I bet I could hurt you more if I told Oga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:58.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代さんよりも—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:01.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大神(おおが)に言ったほうが\Nダメージでかそうで いいかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:04.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）ああっ あ… あ…\N（海崎）うそだよ 言わねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.46,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.67,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:08.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふう…\Nでも そういうことだと思うぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:08.55,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,But... that is what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:13.22,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Trying to knock others down a peg\N just means lowering yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:13.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人を落とそうとする行為は\N結局 自分を落とす
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:18.60,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Don't go trampling all the hard work \Nand trust you've built up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:18.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今まで積み重ねてきた努力や信頼を\N自分で踏みにじるな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.23,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,It insults the effort you put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張ってきた自分に 失礼だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,The only way that would make you happy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなまねして\N喜んでいられるのは—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:28.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,is if you were a loser \Nwho'd given up on trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:28.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 頑張ることをあきらめた\N負け犬だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:32.87,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,But I don't think that describes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:32.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 俺は\N狩生が そうだとは思えない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:36.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が知ってる狩生は\N負けん気が強くて—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:36.45,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,The Kariu I know hates losing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.75,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,is curt but kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶっきらぼうだけど 優しくて—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.87,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,and is a hard worker with a strong heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,芯の強い頑張り屋だと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.92,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Because I know how hard you've worked,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張る狩生を見てきたからこそ—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:48.09,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I'm not really mad. Just very, very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:48.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怒るより何より\Nただ ただ 悲しく思った
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:53.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）汚い大人みたいなまね\Nしないでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:53.01,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Don't act like some filthy adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.47,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You're still young!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:56.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ 若いんだ\N頑張ることをあきらめな…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.64,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Don't give up on try—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が分かるのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:57.73,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,What would you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.89,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,What the hell are you lecturing me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:00.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 悟ったようなこと言ってんの？\N同い年のくせに！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.06,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,We're the same age!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.44,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I {\i1}did{\i0} try!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張ったわよ！\Nでも 全然 かなわない！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.86,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,But I couldn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:04.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かなわないどころか—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.28,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Not only that, they don't \Neven see me as a rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:07.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライバルだとすら\N認識してもらえてないのに！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.53,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Honoka for sports, Hishiro for studies...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）運動では ほのかに\N勉強では 日代に！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.28,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I'm trying desperately to beat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:14.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしは こんなに必死なのに\N何で ２人は涼しい顔で—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.53,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,So why do they act like\NI'm no threat at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.49,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Why am I the only one with problems?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で あたしだけが\Nうまくいかないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:20.08,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I try and try and try and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:19.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら頑張っても\N頑張っても 頑張っても—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張って…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.18,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,No matter how hard I try,\N I get nothing in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張っても 結果が出ない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意味がない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.23,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,It's all pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.69,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,周りと比べるから\N見えにくいだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:46.77,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You're just too busy comparing \Nyourself to others to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Those comparisons aren't the only measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:49.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人と比べた順位だけが\N結果じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.78,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Don't say it's all pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意味ないなんて 否定するな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:57.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You've worked hard and made yourself better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:57.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生は すげえ頑張って\Nその分 ちゃんと成長してる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.79,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,That's what you got in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結果 出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.37,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,So don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:03.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから もう\Nこんなことして 自分を落とすな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.83,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,...put yourself down like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:08.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）そっか あたし…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.71,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.46,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.30,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,...all my hard work...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）ちゃんと頑張れてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:19.14,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,...wasn't pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:19.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意味なく… なかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:24.27,Black Signs,,0,0,0,,Nurse's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.65,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）落ち着いた？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ？ 何が？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.23,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Huh? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.23,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Always gotta act tough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）強がるなあ ほんと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:33.49,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You said no matter how hard you tried...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生は\N“いくら頑張っても”って言うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう いいわよ その話は！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.28,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Stop talking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.60,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,But Hishiro-san's trying, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代さんも 頑張ってると思う
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.66,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,She was in the staff room this late...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）こんな時間まで\N職員室にいたって—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:45.21,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I bet she had questions \Nfor the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:45.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ 先生に\N質問とかしてたんじゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:48.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代さんだって\Nうまくいかない部分 あるんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:48.13,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,There are things even she doesn't find easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:49.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）にたー…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.63,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,She's really awkward, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）不器用だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:57.22,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I think you've got the \Nwrong idea about her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:56.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生は たぶん 日代さんを\N誤解してる部分もあると思う
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.43,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You've never really talked to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんまり ちゃんと話したこと\Nないだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:05.14,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Next time you get a chance, \Nask her to smile for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:05.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度 機会があったら\N“笑ってみて”って言ってみ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.94,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:06.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,笑って？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.73,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,It's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:08.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面白い子だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）うわあ…\N説教たれちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.15,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I just lectured her like an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:14.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オッサンくせえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.03,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Don't give up on trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:16.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“頑張ることを\Nあきらめないでくれ”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.74,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Talk about pot calling the kettle black.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:19.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんつうブーメランだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:23.54,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I'm one to talk,\Nconsidering I gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:23.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よくもまあ\Nあきらめたやつが偉そうに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.88,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Wh-What's up, Hishiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっ どうしたの？ 日代さん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:36.22,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:36.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）海崎さんを待ってました
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.76,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,There's something bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）どうしても\N気になったことがあって—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えても分からなくて—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:43.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Thinking about it didn't get me anywhere,\Nso I waited to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞きたくて 待ってました
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:48.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Why did Kariu-san have my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:48.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生さんが 私のかばんを\N持っていたんでしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.48,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I've thought about it a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:51.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）\Nいろいろ考えましたが—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:54.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正直 “取られた”という\N答えしか出てこなくて—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:56.11,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,but all I can think of is that \Nshe stole it, so I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,困惑しています
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.24,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:01.74,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Kariu-san and my eyes \Nhave been meeting often lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生さんとは 最近\Nよく目が合うし—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:04.54,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,and every time, I've made sure to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:04.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目が合えば 笑いかけるよう\N心がけていて—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:08.25,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,So I thought we were friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:08.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲良くなれていってるものだと\N思っていたので
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:11.21,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Th-Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）か… 考えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:16.05,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,What the hell should I tell this \Nmalice-free tone-deaf communicator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:13.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この 一切 悪気のない\N超コミュ音痴に—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何て答えるのが正解なんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:24.06,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Sh-She thought it was dangerous \Nto leave the bag lying in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:24.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廊下にかばんを放っておくのは\N危ないって思ったんだと…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:27.52,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,So she thought she'd take care of it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:27.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで とりあえず\N保護しておこうと 狩生が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:33.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですか\Nそれならよかったです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.31,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.11,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.07,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Now that I know the reason,\NI feel a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理由が分かって すっきりしました
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:39.53,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I knew she couldn't have tried to steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取るだなんて—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなはずないと\N思ったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:44.24,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,But I couldn't think of anything else.\NI'm ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:42.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 他に考えが\N及ばなかった自分が—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:44.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恥ずかしいです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:52.00,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Is getting rid of all the thorns in\Nsomeone's path really what's best for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夜明(よあけ)）石をどけた きれいな道を\N歩かせてあげることが—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:52.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はたして\N本人のためになるのかどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.00,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめん 今のは うそだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.30,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,That was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:03.60,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Kariu took your bag to\Ncause problems for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:02.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）狩生は 日代さんの\Nかばんを持ち逃げして—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,困らせようとした
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.14,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Why would she...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:08.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シルバーピンが欲しかったから—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.02,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,She wanted the silver pin,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:11.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しっととか 悔しさとか…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:11.40,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,so she was jealous and frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.11,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Kariu-san wants this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:15.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生さんは\Nこれが欲しいということでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.53,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Holy crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）やばい 大神以上の鈍感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:17.99,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,She's even denser than Oga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では これをあげたら\N友達になれますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:21.49,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Then if I give her this,\N can we be friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）ねえよ\N（日代）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.49,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.41,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からないです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.66,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Does Kariu-san hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:29.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 狩生さんから\N憎まれてるんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.46,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess you wouldn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 日代さんには\N分かんねえだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:33.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）グサッ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（女子生徒）日代さんさあ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:35.79,Flashback Dialogue,Classmate,0,0,0,,Hishiro-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:39.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら 頭良くても\Nその鈍感さは どうかと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:39.92,Flashback Dialogue,Classmate,0,0,0,,for someone so smart,\N you can be really dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.43,Flashback Dialogue,Classmate,0,0,0,,You haven't noticed that\Neveryone's mad at you, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんながイラついてるの\N気づいてないでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:47.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を言ったら怒るとか—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:49.39,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I don't understand what I say \Nthat makes people so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:52.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の気持ちとか そういうのが\N全然 分からないんです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:52.31,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I don't understand how they feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:56.44,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I know that's because \NI haven't properly socialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと 人付き合いを\Nしてこなかったせいだと—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自覚しています
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.53,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I've tried to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:12:01.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学ぼうと 私なりに\N調べたりもするんですけど—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:01.45,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I've tried to study up on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:03.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体 何が正解なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.61,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,but I just don't know what's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:07.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うーん 難しいよな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.87,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,That's a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:10.04,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,There is no right answer for getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:09.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人付き合いに\N決まった正解なんてないし—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.00,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Different people require different answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手が違えば\N正解も違うだろうし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:17.84,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Different people... \Nrequire different answers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:17.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）\N相手が違えば 正解も違う？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:19.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）ごめん\N悩ませるつもりは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.01,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't mean to overload you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:25.26,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I'm going to wait for Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:25.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）\N私 狩生さんを待ちます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）えっ\N（日代）このままでは 嫌です
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.93,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I can't leave this be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:31.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 ちゃんと 狩生さんと\N友達になりたいです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:31.35,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I want to be her friend for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:34.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,But I don't know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:34.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも どうしたらいいのか\N分かりません
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:38.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正解も解き方も分からないなら\N直接 聞きます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:38.40,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,If I don't know the right answer... \NI'll just ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.07,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Like you're asking a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）んなっ…\N先生に質問するみたいなノリで？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.78,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,One more question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:44.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと １つ 聞きたいことが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.83,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,When I saw your hands wrapped \Nprotectively around her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:49.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）狩生さんをかばう\N海崎さんの手を見た時に—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気持ちが もやっとしたのは\Nなぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:52.16,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,why did I feel a pang?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:55.00,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ やっぱりいいです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:58.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一度に 多くの問題を抱えるのは\N効率が悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:59.00,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,It's ineffective to deal \Nwith many problems at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずは １つずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.42,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,One at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.09,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Please go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海崎さんは お帰りください
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.93,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I think I have to take care of this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分で何とかしなければ\Nならないことだと思いますので
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:09.43,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,G-Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）わ 分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.47,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,See you later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ… お先に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:24.82,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）って！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:28.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな状況 放って帰れるかー！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.82,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Like I can possibly just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.28,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Will she be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫かなあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夜明）大丈夫ですかねえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.99,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,I dunno, will she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.29,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:36.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）何で いる！\N（夜明）今さら変なこと言いますね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.71,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,You should be used to this by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:39.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海崎さんのいる所\N常に 僕ありですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:39.71,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Wherever you go, I go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:42.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）キメえ！\N（夜明）声 大きいですって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:40.67,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.38,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Keep your voice down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:43.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと“キモい”は\Nひどいです
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:43.92,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,And don't be mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:48.05,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be \Nwatching me, not Hishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:48.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたの役目は\N日代さんじゃなくて俺の観察だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:53.02,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,The influence your choices \Nhave on those around you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:52.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海崎さんの選択が\N周囲に与える影響
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:57.19,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,is also a target of my observations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:57.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その行く末\Nそれもまた 観察対象ですので
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:05.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）\N狩生さん 待ってました
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.90,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.15,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.41,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,An ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）待ち伏せ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.04,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Oh. that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:20.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしが 日代のかばんを\N持ってたことは バレてるんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:20.17,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,She knows I had her bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.00,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,So this is an interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ってことは 尋問…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）狩生さん\N（狩生）はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:24.71,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに このシルバーピンが\N欲しいんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.34,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Do you want this silver pin that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.01,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Right for the jugular!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎･夜明）\Nいきなり あおった！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）\N狩生さんが 私のかばんを—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:36.23,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I heard you tried to run off with my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ち逃げしようとしたことを\N聞きました
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.85,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Kaizaki-san told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海崎さんから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:38.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）あいつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:38.69,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,That jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）\N俺の告げ口 バラされたー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.02,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,She ratted me out for ratting Kariu out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:44.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,When I asked why you would do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:44.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）なぜ そんなことを\Nしたのかと聞いたら—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シルバーピンが理由だと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.40,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,he said your motive was this silver pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.78,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,So I asked if we could \Nbe friends if I gave you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ これを譲れば\N友達になれるかと聞いたら—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“ねえよ”と言われました
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.99,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,and he said no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:54.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）ないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.28,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Yeah, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生さん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.20,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.46,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のことが お嫌いですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.46,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.42,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:06.38,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Then why did you take my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:06.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では なぜ かばんを？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:10.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌いではない相手に\Nそのような行動を起こす意図は？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:09.88,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Why would you do that \Nto someone you don't hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.89,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,She straight up asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）どストレート
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よくも まあ\Nああも ずけずけ聞けるな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.14,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I dunno how she can keep asking this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:17.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の心 えぐられねえのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.35,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Doesn't it hurt her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:19.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代さんですからねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.39,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Well, it {\i1}is{\i0} Hishiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.40,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:22.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）逃げるな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.19,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Don't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,答えろ 狩生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.65,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Answer, Kariu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.28,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:31.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）\N誰が… もう 逃げるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.49,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,...running anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.57,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）嫌いよ\N（日代）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:36.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）どれだけ頑張っても\Nかなわなくて—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.66,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,No matter how hard I try, I can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:39.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしが欲しかったものを\N手に入れて—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.71,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,You took what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:42.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしが欲しかった場所を\N手に入れて！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.21,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,You stood where I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.95,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,And ever since you won, you've always,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ち誇ったように いつも—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:47.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも あたしをバカにして笑う\Nあんたが 大っ嫌いよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.63,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,always flashed that mocking smile,\N so of course I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:58.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）\Nバカになんてしたことないです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.10,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I've never mocked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:01.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,してるじゃない！\N目が合うたびに いつもいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.64,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,You do! Every time our eyes meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:02.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）してません\N（狩生）してる！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:02.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:02.77,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,You do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.90,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Why would I ever do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ 私が\N狩生さんをバカにする必要が…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:06.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）知るか！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:06.82,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:08.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）\N何 すっとぼけてるのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.03,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,How can you deny it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんなに 何度も\N人を こけにしておいて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.20,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,That constant stream of sneers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:14.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目が合うたびに\N話すたびに いつもいつも！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.37,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Every time our eyes meet, \Nevery time we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:18.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度 機会があったら\N“笑ってみて”って言ってみ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:18.62,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Next time you get a chance, \Nask her to smile for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:21.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.91,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:25.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）日代 ちょっと笑ってみて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:23.62,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Hishiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.96,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Smile for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.51,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:30.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何ですか？ 急に\N待ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:33.93,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Hold on. I'm trying to think \Nof a reason I'd mock—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:33.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 私が狩生さんをバカにする\N理由を考えているところ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）いいから！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.01,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:38.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人と目が合った時に ニコッとする\N程度の笑顔でいいから！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:38.26,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,A normal smile, like you'd do \Nif your eyes met someone's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.14,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）今 引きましたよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.78,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,You just freaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:53.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）えっ？ あっ いや\Nちょっ… 待って 整理する
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:50.57,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:53.20,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Er... wait... let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:56.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）えっ？ えっ？\N今のが 日代の中での笑顔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.91,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.70,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Hishiro thinks that's a smile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:59.58,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,She was trying for a friendly smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:59.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの子\Nあれで愛想笑いのつもりなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.08,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I thought Kaizaki was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）てっきり\N海崎のうそだと思ってたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:06.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）もう１回 笑ってみて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.00,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.71,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戻して
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:10.63,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）もう１回\N（日代）へへ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この どヘタクソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.22,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Oh my god, you suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.18,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,How is that a smile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それの どこが笑顔よ！\N鏡 見たことあんの!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.60,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Have you even looked in a mirror?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:21.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな笑顔 無言で向けられた人が\Nどう思うと思ってんのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:21.93,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea\Nhow it makes people feel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:24.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたし てっきり バカに\Nされてるんだと ずっと思ってた！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.69,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I thought you were \Nmocking me this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:29.90,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I have been smiling in the hope \Nthat we could be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は ずっと—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:29.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生さんと友達になりたい一心で\N笑ってました
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:42.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）何 この子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.37,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Wow, this girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:44.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんだけ不器用なのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.66,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,How awkward can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:49.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の長所は 頭がいいところです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:49.38,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,My strong point is I'm smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）分からないところがあれば\N自分で調べ—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.92,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,If I don't understand something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:57.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも分からなければ質問し\N解決に努めます
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:56.93,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I look into it on my own, \Nand if I still don't get it, I ask until I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:00.68,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,My weak point is that \NI'm not interested in other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,短所は\N周囲に全く興味がないことです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:02.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎･夜明）\N言い切った！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.47,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,She said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:06.39,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Because of that, I don't know \Nhow to interact with anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:06.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）そのせいで\N人との付き合い方が分からず—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:09.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おそらく 多くの人に\N迷惑をかけてきました
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.40,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,and I must have caused \Nlots of problems for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:13.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど 今は こんな自分を\N変えていきたいと思っています
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:13.94,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,But right now, I'm trying to change myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:18.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生さん こんな私ですが—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:18.32,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Kariu-san, that's who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:22.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,友達になって… くれませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:22.24,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,But would you be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.21,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,It's my pleasure, Hishiro Chizuru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:29.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よろしくね 日代千鶴(ちづる)さん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.17,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,That day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:31.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）あの時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:35.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれも 別に 握手を\N避けられたわけじゃなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:35.63,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,she wasn't intentionally \Nignoring the handshake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:45.35,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Okay, Hishiro Chizuru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:45.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よろしく 日代千鶴さん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも そのかわり！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:51.56,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,But in return, recognize me as your rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:51.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしのこと ライバルだって\Nちゃんと認めてよね！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次は負けないから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.61,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I won't lose next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対 あたしが\Nシルバーピンを取ってみせるから！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:55.99,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I'll definitely take that silver pin from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:59.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに欲しいなら\N次のテストで お譲りしますが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:59.32,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,If you want it, you can have it next test...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:02.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）そうじゃないんだって！\N欲しいけど そうじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:02.16,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Don't you dare! I want it, but not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手加減なんかしたら\N即 絶交してやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.62,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,If you hold back, we're not friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.50,Not Sign,,0,0,0,,Not Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.50,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）あと…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:12.25,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回のことは\N本当に ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:13.42,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I won't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:13.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 二度としない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.05,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:15.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:19.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）許します
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.17,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:23.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,友達… ですから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.68,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,After all, we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:30.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ ちゃんと笑えるんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.69,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Whoa, so you can actually smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）いつだって笑えてますが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.44,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,But I smile all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）うそつけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.52,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.90,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You told Hishiro about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:42.78,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,But thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,What'd you take a picture for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:45.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 撮ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:49.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＪＫにLIME(ライム)もらって\Nにやける被験者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.50,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,A test subject grinning \Nbecause a high school girl LIMEd him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:50.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,報告書用に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.53,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,For my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:51.54,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:53.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）消せ！ 大体 何で\N俺ん家(ち)で飲んでんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.54,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Why are we drinking at my place, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:54.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 これ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:54.42,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,What is all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:56.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.25,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:59.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海崎さんが ２人の仲を取り持った\Nめでたい日でしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.92,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,You helped them become friends.\NLet's celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:02.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん… 明日も学校なんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.34,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,We've got school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:05.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニートやってた割に\Nまじめなんですよねえ 海崎さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:06.26,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,For an ex-NEET, you sure are serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）\Nニートじゃねえ フリーター！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.06,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Not NEET! I was a part-timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Yoake-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜明さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:15.56,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Was what I told Kariu\N really the right thing to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:15.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が 狩生にかけた言葉は\N正しかったんだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:18.57,Black Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,1)}{\an5}Resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:17.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって 現実は—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:20.90,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,In reality, I couldn't grow up, \Nand became a NEET.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:20.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大人になりきれなかった\N甘い俺が ニートになり—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:26.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他人を落としたあいつらは たぶん\N今も 悠々と仕事を続けてる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:25.57,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,And those awful bullies probably \Nstill have their jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.75,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I know the real truth is uglier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:30.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我ながら\Nきれい事を吐いたなあと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:33.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに\Nきれい事だったかもしれません
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:34.17,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it wasn't the ugly truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも うそじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.88,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,But it wasn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:39.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本心から出た言葉なんだから\Nいいじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:39.42,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,It's what you really meant, \Nso isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:43.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生さんが 社会に出て\Nつまずいた時—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:43.38,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,When she's out in the \Nreal world and stumbles,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:48.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰とは思い出せないけど 自分を\Nしかってくれた人がいたなあと—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:48.43,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,she'll remember someone \Nyelling at her, if not who.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:53.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日の記憶は きっと彼女の中に\N残り続けるんじゃないかと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:53.31,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,I think what happened today \Nwill stay with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:55.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:55.73,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:21:00.15,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Though, really, it was \Nthe pot calling the kettle black!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:59.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 盛大なブーメラン\N投げてるなとは思いましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:02.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“人と比べた順位だけが\N結果じゃない”？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:03.24,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yelling at her for comparing \Nherself to others!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,周囲との差に焦って—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:07.57,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Says the man so worried about appearances, \Nhe pretended he still had a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:06.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕事してるフリしてた人が\Nよく言いますわ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:07.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）グサッ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:10.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっせえ！\Nちゃんと 自分でも思ったわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.58,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Shut up! I thought the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうです？ リライフ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.58,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,So? Are you liking ReLIFE?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:17.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分を いい感じで\N見つめ直せてます？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:17.17,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Is it letting you take a long,\Nhard look at yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:23.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その 何でもお見通し感が\Nほんっと ムカつくわーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:23.59,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,The way you see through everything \Nis seriously driving me nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:48.68,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Rena, see any empty seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:48.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉来(たまらい)）玲奈(れな)\N空いてる席 あった？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:52.55,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Say, Honoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:52.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほのか あのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:57.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:56.89,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:57.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:22:57.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:02.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ お昼\N一緒に食べてあげてもいいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:02.19,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I-I don't mind eating lunch with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:06.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に大丈夫です\N私 １人 好きですし
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:05.03,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I'm fine like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:06.61,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I like being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.02,0:23:09.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがダメなんでしょ！\N変わりたいんでしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:08.70,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Isn't that the problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:09.74,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Don't you want to change?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:12.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）そうでした
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:11.95,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:15.33,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Then, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:16.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では お願いします\Nありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:16.49,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:18.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ お礼なんかいいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:18.16,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,D-Don't thank me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:19.71,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,We're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.49,0:23:21.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,友達なんだから！\N普通なんだから！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:21.29,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,This is normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:40.14,Next Episode,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:27.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）日代は まず\N笑顔の練習からね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:28.09,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hishiro, you need to first\Npractice how to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:29.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）にやあ…\N（狩生）だからそうじゃないってば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:28.84,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.05,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:31.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）\Nできてるつもりですが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:31.76,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I thought I was doing it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:33.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生さん\N手本を見せてください
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:33.76,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show me how it's done, Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:35.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）えっ？ 仕方ないなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:36.02,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:40.14,Next Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,1)}This Isn't the First Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:37.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）キッ… キラッ\N（日代）カタいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:36.68,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:37.64,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.51,0:23:39.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）\Nあんたに言われたくないわよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:39.52,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna hear that from you!
